articles.author: Alex Tabet
articles.title: European soccer heavyweights clash in Champions League final - NBC News
articles.description: Inter Milan and Paris Saint-Germain will meet at the UEFA Champions League final in Munich on Saturday to compete for club soccer’s most prestigious trophy.
